Introduction

LABELUP was an upcoming five-member girl group under Yedam Entertainment.
The group held a release event for the pre-debut fan single "Beautiful Tomorrow" in Japan on December 27, 2019, which was eventually released on digital platforms on March 25, 2020.

They disbanded on January 31, 2021 following long and serious discussions amongst the members.
